00:49:16,578 --> 00:49:19,331
on the medical center's website,

663
00:49:19,414 --> 00:49:21,833
and thus, we have a duty to comply.

664
00:49:23,752 --> 00:49:25,003
Which improper deeds?

665
00:49:25,587 --> 00:49:28,590
