685
00:50:27,816 --> 00:50:30,652
As I said, the artificial joints'
life span is numbered.

686
00:50:30,736 --> 00:50:32,904
Currently, it's between 10 to 15 years.

687
00:50:42,330 --> 00:50:43,290
